title: Squash Dressing
ingredients: ["4 c. cooked squash", "1 stick oleo", "1 can cream of chicken soup", "1 box Stove Top dressing", "1 onion, chopped"]
directions: ["Mix all ingredients together.", "Put in 11 x 13-inch greased dish.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 25 minutes."]

title: Corned Beef And Noodles
ingredients: ["12 oz. can corned beef, broken up", "1/4 lb. American cheese (about 1 c.), broken", "1 can cream of chicken soup", "1 c. milk", "1/2 c. chopped onion", "8 oz. noodles, cooked and drained"]
directions: ["Alternate in layers in greased baking dish.", "Top with 3/4 cup crumbs.", "Bake 30 to 40 minutes at 375\u00b0."]

title: Baked Potato Salad
ingredients: ["8 medium potatoes, cubed", "1/2 lb. bacon, fried and crumbled", "1/2 lb. Velveeta cheese, cubed", "1 1/2 c. Hellmann's mayonnaise", "1/4 c. finely chopped onion", "salt and pepper"]
directions: ["Mix all together well; put in a 9 x 13-inch baking pan.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 1 hour covered.", "Stir every 20 minutes."]

title: Funnel Cakes
ingredients: ["2 eggs", "1 1/2 c. milk", "2 c. flour", "1 tsp. baking powder", "1/2 tsp. salt", "powdered sugar", "cinnamon powder (optional)"]
directions: ["Heat 2-inches deep of oil in skillet.", "Heat oil until hot, but not smoking.", "Take batter, pour it through funnel into hot oil, moving in a circular motion, then crisscross until you've made a cake the size of a plate or smaller.", "When lightly browned, remove and drain on paper towels.", "Dredge or sprinkle in powdered sugar and sprinkle with cinnamon powder.", "Best when eaten warm."]
